lenders.name: Andrew Senior
lenders.occupation: Global Experts in Creative Economy development
lenders.loan_because: In our work we continue to meet remarkable creative people who continually find it difficult to access sources of funding to support the development of their creative business. There are very few vehicles for supporting business development in least developed, developing and emerging economies. Kiva is one, which is why we support it.
lenders.occupational_info: We work with governments and foundations, often in emerging and developing economies, to provide support for the creation of policies and interventions that stimulate the development of a competitive and sustainable creative economy. At the heart of our work is a passion for entrepreneurship in the creative sector, be that in terms of business start-ups or the creation of scaleable businesses that can create employment for those that can't set up their own business. We work to ensure that the potential of the creative economy is better recognised and understood and that the creative sector is better placed to make the unique economic, social and cultural contribution of which it is capable.
